---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About - Clay & Co.">
  <section class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-amber-50 to-stone-100">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold text-stone-800 mb-4">Our Story</h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-stone-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          From a small Brooklyn apartment to a thriving pottery studio, Clay & Co. has been bringing handcrafted beauty to New York for over 8 years.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center mb-16">
        <div>
          <div class="w-full h-96 bg-gradient-to-br from-amber-200 to-amber-400 rounded-lg"></div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-stone-800 mb-6">Meet Sarah Chen</h2>
          <p class="text-stone-600 mb-4">
            Founded in 2016, Clay & Co. began as a passion project in my tiny Brooklyn apartment. What started as a creative outlet after long days in corporate marketing has grown into a full-time pottery studio and community hub.
          </p>
          <p class="text-stone-600 mb-4">
            With a BFA in Ceramics from Parsons and years of experience in various clay techniques, I specialize in functional pottery that brings joy to everyday moments. Every piece that leaves our studio is crafted with intention and care.
          </p>
          <p class="text-stone-600">
            When I'm not at the wheel, you can find me exploring NYC's incredible food scene, searching for inspiration in museums, or teaching pottery workshops to spread the love of handmade ceramics.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
