            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Design</h3>
            <p class="text-stone-600">Every piece begins with a sketch and careful consideration of form and function.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-amber-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
              <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-amber-600">2</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Shape</h3>
            <p class="text-stone-600">Using the potter's wheel and hand-building techniques to create the perfect form.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-amber-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
              <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-amber-600">3</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Glaze</h3>
            <p class="text-stone-600">Applying custom glazes that enhance both beauty and durability.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-amber-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
              <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-amber-600">4</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Fire</h3>
            <p class="text-stone-600">High-temperature firing transforms clay into durable, beautiful ceramic.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-stone-800 mb-6">Our Philosophy</h2>
          <p class="text-stone-600 mb-4">
            We believe that everyday objects should be beautiful, functional, and made with care. In our fast-paced world, there's something special about slowing down with a handmade mug, feeling its unique texture, and knowing it was created by human hands.
          </p>
          <p class="text-stone-600 mb-4">
